{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"フォーム","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下のページでは、ウェブフォームのアクセシビリティを向上させるさまざまなテクニックを紹介します。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/Accessibility/ARIA_64707ba1917a56654679cbe273e2f4ea\">基本的なフォームのヒント</a>: 値が無効あるいは必須のフィールドに、ヒントや説明を追加します。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\">アラート</a>: アラートを使用して、クライアントサイドの検証で発生したエラーメッセージを示します。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/forms/Multipart_labels\">マルチパートのラベル</a>: 各々のラベル内で制御することにより、複雑なフォームラベルを実現します。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>同様のコンテンツを多く扱っている、<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120801225355/http://yaccessibilityblog.com/library/aria-invalid-form-inputs.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">フォーム検証や ARIA に関する Yahoo! の記事</a>（archive.org より取得）もご覧ください。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"以下のページでは、ウェブフォームのアクセシビリティを向上させるさまざまなテクニックを紹介します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Forms","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Formularios","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Formulaires","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Forms","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Formulários","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Forms","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Forms","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/accessibility/aria/forms","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/accessibility/aria/forms/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"アクセシビリティ"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA